  "prompt": "Which are the best news website in India?",
  "response": "There are several reputable news websites in India that provide comprehensive coverage of national and international events. Here are some of the best:\n\n1. **The Times of India (timesofindia.indiatimes.com)** - One of the largest newspapers in India, it covers a wide range of topics including politics, entertainment, and sports.\n\n2. **The Hindu (thehindu.com)** - Known for its in-depth analysis and quality journalism, The Hindu covers national and international news, and is respected for its editorial stance.\n\n3. **Indian Express (indianexpress.com)** - Another respected news outlet, known for its investigative journalism and detailed reporting on current affairs.\n\n4. **Hindustan Times (hindustantimes.com)** - A leading English-language newspaper that covers a variety of topics including politics, entertainment, and lifestyle.\n\n5. **BBC News India (bbc.com/news/world/india)** - The Indian arm of the BBC provides both national and international news with a global perspective.\n\n6. **Scroll.in (scroll.in)** - An online news website that features a mix of news, opinion, and commentary, often focusing on social issues and culture.\n\n7. **News18 (news18.com)** - A prominent news portal that covers breaking news, politics, entertainment, and sports.\n\n8. **The Wire (thewire.in)** - An independent news website known for its critical analysis and investigative journalism.\n\n9. **Zee News (zeenews.india.com)** - Offers a wide range of news including politics, entertainment, sports, and health.\n\n10. **Alt News (altnews.in)** - A fact-checking website dedicated to combating misinformation and disinformation in Indian news.\n\nThese websites offer a mix of opinion, analysis, and straightforward reporting, catering to different interests and preferences.",
